    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="detail-wrapper">
  <div class="detail-container">
    <div class="detail1">
      <div class="image-box1">
      <img class="box-image1" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1491438590914-bc09fcaaf77a?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1050&q=80">
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>思い出を記録する</h2>
      <p>楽しかった場所や友達との思い出を写真と文章でみんなに伝えよう。</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail2">
      <div class="img-box2">
        <img class="box-image2" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1548585742-de182e9e9378?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1039&q=80">
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>現地の情報を知る</h2>
        <p>既に留学を経験している先輩達の<br>生の声を聞いて充実した留学生活を送ろう。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="footer-wrapper">
  <div class="footer-container">
    <h4 class="ask">お問い合わせはこちら</h4>
    <p>twitter: @ken_768
      <br>email: example.1@email.com</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
jQuery(function(){
  
  $('.top-wrapper').hide().fadeIn(1500);
  $('.top-container').hide().fadeIn(3500);

});

$(function(){
  
  $(window).scroll(function(){
    let scroll = $(window).scrollTop();
    if(scroll > 750){
      $('.footer-wrapper').css("opacity","1");
    }else if(scroll > 550){
      $('.detail-wrapper, .detail-container').fadeIn(2000);
    }else if(scroll > 100){
      $('.about-wrapper, .about-container').fadeIn(2000);
    }else{
      $('.about-wrapper, .about-container').hide();
      $('.detail-wrapper, .detail-container').hide();
      $('.footer-wrapper').css("opacity","0");
    }
      

  });

});



</script>

